description:
University employee Ryouichirou is ordered by the Chairman to take in an exchange student. That exchange student, Qaltaqa, is a native from a developing country who can't understand Japanese! Though he is a warrior of his tribe and a man of great beauty, seeing him afraid of the phone and the TV &ndash; and even the toilet &ndash; Ryouichirou gets fed up&hellip;
But while being called &quot;Ryouichirou&quot; in such a clumsy manner, he has a change of heart!?

[u]Espa&ntilde;ol:[/u]
[spoiler]El rector de la Universidad ordena a Ryouichirou, un empleado de la misma, el recoger a un estudiante de intercambio. Este estudiante, Qaltaqa &iexcl;&iexcl;es un nativo de un pa&iacute;s en desarrollo que no puede entender japon&eacute;s!!. Aunque &eacute;l es un guerrero de su tribu y un hombre de gran belleza, verlo asustado frente al tel&eacute;fono y a la televisi&oacute;n, incluso el retrete, provoca que Ryouichirou se harte&hellip;
Pero mientras est&aacute; siendo llamado &ldquo;Ryouichorou&rdquo; de tal forma torpe, &iexcl;&iquest;&eacute;l cambia de parecer?![/spoiler]

Tora is looking for a job, so he decides to apply for this particular place&hellip;What he didn&rsquo;t know is that this place is a Male&rsquo;s Brothel. Here he meets Shiro, the most requested male prostitute. At the beginning Tora feels reluctant to work in this environment, but the vulnerability aura that surrounds Shiro makes him stay, plus he needs the money. Everything goes well at first, they stablish this sort of friendship, but shortly after that, feelings, desire and painful secrets complicates their already fragile relationship&hellip;

[b][u]Polish / Polski:[/u][/b]
[spoiler]Aby spłacić dług swojej młodszej siostry, Nobutora zgłasza się do nietypowego miejsca w poszukiwaniu zatrudnienia - ekskluzywnego burdelu dla gej&oacute;w. Rozpoczyna pracę jako ochroniarz popularnego chłopaka - Shiro. Nobutora pr&oacute;buje wyznaczyć granicę pomiędzy sobą, a wywyższającym się i napastującym go seksualnie Shiro, stopniowo jednak ta dw&oacute;jka otwiera się względem siebie. Wkr&oacute;tce Shiro zauważa, że Nobutora staje się nim zauroczony...

Timid Yasumori is always wearing half a smile with fear in his eyes as he gets bullied.

Takemi who has had Yasumori on his mind, rescues him, and in the heat of the moment, he confesses his feelings to Yasumori. In reply, Yasumori gives an unexpected answer: &quot;That means you'll submit to me, right?&quot;

While love takes on many different forms, these feelings can't be replaced&mdash; A love story packed with the inconsistent meanings of &quot;love&quot; uniting as one.

After stomach cramps land Muramachi Koharu in a bed at the nurse's office on the very first day at his new school, he suddenly wakes up to find himself on the landing just before the roof door. And there's a student he doesn't know sitting right next to him!

&quot;Where am I? Who are you?&quot;

The student says he's one year Koharu's senior and he leans closer and closer to him&hellip;! He pushes Koharu down&hellip; and suddenly kisses him!

An eternal quest for his true love, against the clock&hellip;
To keep their centuries-old vow.

Five hundred years ago, a vampire prince and a girl fell in love. However, the girl was only human, with a human life-span, and she eventually passed on. In sorrow, the prince searched for a way to turn himself back into a human, to avoid feeling that pain again&hellip; Current day, and the girl has been reborn into a peaceful life, and the prince has found a way to &ldquo;return&rdquo;&hellip; A romantic concerto is about to begin!
